Ques: How can you optimize performance in React app ?
Ans: Performance optimization strategies include:

• Code-splitting with React.lazy().

• Memoizing components with React.memo.

• Debouncing or throttling events like input.

• Using useMemo and useCallback to avoid unnecessary recalculations.

• Implementing error boundaries and lazy loading.

